<br />\n會令被逼罷工又好少投票既犬儒派投建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好多手足因為尋日既大失敗感到灰心<br />\n熱血地和應呢個會逆轉民意既行動<br />\n所以我一直講<br />\n對家完全捉到連登仔性格心態<br />\n得連登得天下，佢地得左<br />\n<br />\n好似我地呢d少數反對逼人大三罷既，會被打成五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ed116270bc16f568acfe5c5e5c4710f3d31847","tid":1690117,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0703fea7ecd122acab8476bf47d0413c8e16a5d1","tid":1690117,"uid":65354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"其實巴士同港鐵車長肯罷工已經可以全民罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"上次黨鐵車長罷左<br />\n但無影響<br />\n<br />\n因為黨鐵搵左退休車長返黎開"},{"pid":"bd62250b9b34dac06757ade76169c846565f0275","tid":1690117,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b155c11c3d0710a87f85132b9b5f889fe9f4973","tid":1690117,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"8月5各區開花其實幾成功 <br />\n一兩日就可以<br />\n不過重點係要點持續<br />\n<br />\n加上好多襯黃公司都係只限於扣假嘅罷工<br />\n何況藍到發黑嗰啲"},{"pid":"cd8e3583dc37a3e72309e1a760f79c9f2c0494e3","tid":1690117,"uid":298072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0703fea7ecd122acab8476bf47d0413c8e16a5d1","tid":1690117,"uid":65354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"其實巴士同港鐵車長肯罷工已經可以全民罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"不如眾籌課罷工金，200萬人1人1千就有20億可以開公司養起被清算車長"},{"pid":"729e3e43e3656cbad3b8b63f1b460b2eb4b942d1","tid":1690117,"uid":59676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T0